{"word":"G2230 - ἡγεμονεύω - hēgemoneúō - hayg-em-on-yoo'-o - Be governor","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἡγεμονεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hēgemoneúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hayg-em-on-yoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be governor</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தேசாதிபதியாக ஆளுகை செய்"},{"paragraph":"1. to be leader, to lead the way"},{"paragraph":"2. to rule, command: to be governor of a province"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2232 - ἡγεμών - hēgemṓn - hayg-em-ohn'/2232\">G2232</a>; to <i>act as ruler:</i> - be governor.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}